						<summary>

						<p>On the east wall of the Bhairava shrine in the Vālīśvara temple.</p>						

						<p>Year 2.</p>						

						<p>This inscription records an order of Madhurāntaka Pottappi Chōḷa regarding the remission of portion of the tax realised in kind from the different classes of land <hi rend="italic">viz tiruviḍaiyāṭṭam, paḷḷichandam, agarapaṟṟu, vanniyappaṟṟu, jīvitappaṟṟu</hi> and <hi rend="italic">paḍaipaṟṟu</hi> from the month of Aippaśi in the 2nd year.</p>						

						</summary>
					</msContents>
